name: Datasciencecourse$
description: Practical data science is the study and practice of how we can extract insight and knowledge from large amounts of data. It is a burgeoning field, currently attracting substantial demand from both academia and industry. This course provides a practical introduction to the “full stack” of data science analysis, including data collection and processing, data visualization and presentation, and statistical model building using machine learning. Topics covered include: collecting and processing data using relational methods, time series approaches, graph and network models, free text analysis, and spatial geographic
